279
00:16:31,620 --> 00:16:32,700
When the late Emperor deceased,

280
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:35,020
Eighth Prince was overwhelmed by grief

281
00:16:36,180 --> 00:16:37,420
and had mental disorder,

282
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:40,580
talking nonsense and acting crazily.

283
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,780
He has become better after years of recovering,

284
00:16:45,460 --> 00:16:46,660
but I’m worried that

285
00:16:47,980 --> 00:16:49,420
he’ll have the old issue back

286
00:16:50,180 --> 00:16:51,260
if he gets exhausted from attending the court.

287
00:16:52,980 --> 00:16:53,900
Later, you take some Physicians

288
00:16:54,260 --> 00:16:55,780
from the royal hospital

289
00:16:55,780 --> 00:16:56,740
to see him.

290
00:16:57,940 --> 00:16:58,460
Yes, ma’am.

291
00:16:58,540 --> 00:16:59,340
His Majesty is here.

292
00:16:59,900 --> 00:17:00,700
Your Majesty.

293
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:01,660
What are you doing here?

294
00:17:03,620 --> 00:17:05,820
A few days ago, my mother

295
00:17:06,340 --> 00:17:07,980
sent some local products from Daizhou

296
00:17:08,340 --> 00:17:10,340
and some fur of top quality.

297
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:11,820
So I thought

298
00:17:11,980 --> 00:17:13,100
I can take them here first

299
00:17:13,100 --> 00:17:14,260
and see if Your Majesty like them.

300
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:18,500
But then I met with Lady Yang
overstepping her position.

301
00:17:19,380 --> 00:17:21,860
She came here without being summoned.

302
00:17:22,500 --> 00:17:23,780
And she even stole

303
00:17:23,980 --> 00:17:25,540
something from the Hall.

304
00:17:26,500 --> 00:17:27,460
Your Majesty,

305
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:29,140
I came here to give you

306
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:30,780
the fixed socks and vests.

307
00:17:31,540 --> 00:17:32,980
I’m worried you need to use them soon.

308
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:34,140
But,

309
00:17:34,420 --> 00:17:35,820
she doesn’t even let me explain

310
00:17:35,820 --> 00:17:36,900
and accuses me for stealing.

311
00:17:37,300 --> 00:17:38,620
Such an injustice.

312
00:17:38,740 --> 00:17:39,980
I’d rather die

313
00:17:39,980 --> 00:17:41,340
than being wronged like this.

314
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:43,420
Who wronged you?

315
00:17:44,180 --> 00:17:45,820
When you went out of the Hall,

316
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:47,780
the painted wooden box you
were holding in your hand.

317
00:17:48,150 --> 00:17:48,790
That...

318
00:17:49,220 --> 00:17:51,180
I picked that box especially

319
00:17:51,460 --> 00:17:53,540
for containing desserts and candied fruits.

320
00:17:54,100 --> 00:17:56,220
You think I’m a fool or blind?

321
00:17:56,220 --> 00:17:57,140
Don’t I know that?

322
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:58,820
I always make dessert and snacks

323
00:17:58,820 --> 00:18:00,260
for His Majesty.

324
00:18:00,500 --> 00:18:02,180
He likes what I make.

325
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:03,460
I just saw some

326
00:18:03,700 --> 00:18:05,140
new candied fruits and desserts

327
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:05,740
on his desk,

328
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:07,060
so I wanted to take it back

329
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:08,820
and look into it.

330
00:18:09,660 --> 00:18:10,580
Nonsense.

331
00:18:11,380 --> 00:18:14,500
Who appointed you

332
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:16,300
to manage the desserts and candied fruits?

333
00:18:17,180 --> 00:18:19,820
Besides, the food

334
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:21,780
of His Majesty should be handled by
some specific person.

335
00:18:22,460 --> 00:18:24,860
Are you bullying me for being a new people here?

336
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:26,140
Alright,

337
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:28,460
let’s talk about this

338
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:29,300
in front of Her Majesty!

339
00:18:30,020 --> 00:18:31,340
Her Majesty picked you

340
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:32,540
for His Majesty,

341
00:18:32,780 --> 00:18:34,140
so no doubt whatever you say

342
00:18:34,140 --> 00:18:34,980
or do is right.

343
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:36,500
But I

344
00:18:36,740 --> 00:18:38,740
I have nothing to offer to His Majesty
but my sincere heart.

345
00:18:39,100 --> 00:18:40,500
I want him to have better food

346
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:41,460
and better clothes.

347
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:44,420
I have no idea that this would irritate you.

348
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:45,820
You, you…

349
00:18:48,660 --> 00:18:49,460
Alright, enough,

350
00:18:50,580 --> 00:18:52,220
get up, Jinrui.

351
00:18:53,820 --> 00:18:54,780
Come on, Empress.

352
00:18:55,580 --> 00:18:56,500
Sit next to me.

353
00:18:58,380 --> 00:19:00,220
I was going to talk about the
candied fruits with you.

354
00:19:00,820 --> 00:19:01,780
I need the Empress

355
00:19:01,780 --> 00:19:02,820
to lead all the concubines

356
00:19:02,820 --> 00:19:03,780
to do something.

357
00:19:04,340 --> 00:19:05,380
Liu E,

358
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:08,780
you malicious woman!

359
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:12,660
You want to take away the state from the Zhaos!

360
00:19:13,020 --> 00:19:14,420
= The wife of Eighth Prince =
Brother.

361
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:18,100
I’m not sick!

362
00:19:20,980 --> 00:19:22,620
I’m not sick!

363
00:19:23,820 --> 00:19:25,020
Bastard!

364
00:19:26,180 --> 00:19:29,260
He did have

365
00:19:29,260 --> 00:19:30,180
his old issue back.

366
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:35,620
Prince always feels

367
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:38,060
heartache

368
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:39,260
and dizzy these days.

369
00:19:40,660 --> 00:19:42,340
Empress Dowager is worried

370
00:19:42,340 --> 00:19:43,540
about his conditions.

371
00:19:44,300 --> 00:19:45,020
So she asked me to

372
00:19:45,020 --> 00:19:47,060
take some imperial doctors from the royal hospital

373
00:19:47,140 --> 00:19:48,980
and these extremely rare herbs

374
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:50,540
to visit the prince.

375
00:19:50,860 --> 00:19:54,340
She’s stealing our state!

376
00:19:54,740 --> 00:19:56,340
It’s more important to recover his health.

377
00:19:56,980 --> 00:19:58,220
Empress Dowager said that

378
00:19:58,500 --> 00:19:59,980
if Physicians confirmed that

379
00:20:00,260 --> 00:20:01,980
he is ill,

380
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:04,780
he should rest at home these days

381
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:08,260
and be served by Physicians.

382
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:09,660
No need for him to attend the court

383
00:20:09,860 --> 00:20:11,140
or go to the palace.

384
00:20:23,180 --> 00:20:24,980
Why are you still serving so much?

385
00:20:25,340 --> 00:20:26,820
Didn’t I tell you before?

386
00:20:27,620 --> 00:20:30,260
All meals served in the palace must be cut in half

387
00:20:30,740 --> 00:20:31,820
so save the money

388
00:20:31,820 --> 00:20:33,420
for buying food and medicines

389
00:20:33,420 --> 00:20:34,380
for people suffering from the flood in Qionghe.

390
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:37,300
We’ve already removed the crabs.

391
00:20:38,180 --> 00:20:39,940
His Majesty said

392
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:43,020
all the deduction goes under him.

393
00:20:43,220 --> 00:20:44,860
Yours can’t be scanted.

394
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:46,260
Just removing one dish

395
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:48,060
every meal for you

396
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:49,620
is enough.

397
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:57,300
I don’t have much appetite these days.

398
00:20:58,300 --> 00:21:00,100
I feel sick when I see all the
greasy fish and meat.

399
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:01,900
Take them away

400
00:21:03,060 --> 00:21:04,660
and give them to the vassals.

401
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:06,580
Yes.

402
00:21:08,180 --> 00:21:09,060
Your Majesty.

403
00:21:09,260 --> 00:21:11,100
The Empress comes to greet you

404
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:12,780
with Lady Yang,

405
00:21:12,780 --> 00:21:13,980
Lady Shang and some other ladies.

406
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:15,900
Send them in.

407
00:21:16,060 --> 00:21:16,740
Yes.

408
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:20,060
Come on, have some.

409
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:23,460
These brewed plums

410
00:21:23,500 --> 00:21:25,380
and the stuffing inside the dessert

411
00:21:25,580 --> 00:21:27,220
are brewed with

412
00:21:27,340 --> 00:21:28,820
herbs of top quality.

413
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:31,700
It can promoting fluid, reducing phlegm,

414
00:21:31,740 --> 00:21:33,500
moisten the lungs and quench thirst.

415
00:21:33,620 --> 00:21:35,700
His Majesty really likes it.

416
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:36,980
His Majesty said

417
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:38,380
it’s his favorite taste

418
00:21:38,380 --> 00:21:39,700
since he was a kid.

419
00:21:41,540 --> 00:21:43,540
After the late Emperor deceased,

420
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:46,940
there are some desserts, biscuits
and candied fruits

421
00:21:47,180 --> 00:21:50,540
in the palace,

422
00:21:50,780 --> 00:21:52,460
but the taste is not the one he wants.

423
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:56,100
His Majesty asked me

424
00:21:56,220 --> 00:21:58,220
to send some to you,

425
00:21:58,260 --> 00:21:59,540
see if it’s the same taste

426
00:21:59,660 --> 00:22:01,380
of what Madam Li

427
00:22:01,380 --> 00:22:02,660
did before.

428
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:04,340
Madam Li?

429
00:22:05,780 --> 00:22:07,340
The one who

430
00:22:07,340 --> 00:22:08,580
served you before.

431
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:11,660
His Majesty also said

432
00:22:11,780 --> 00:22:13,700
after she was sent to the Mausoleum,

433
00:22:14,060 --> 00:22:15,740
the taste was gone.

434
00:22:16,500 --> 00:22:17,740
I thought

435
00:22:18,460 --> 00:22:20,620
she’s not here anymore,

436
00:22:20,940 --> 00:22:22,980
but the receipt shouldn’t be difficult to find.

437
00:22:24,060 --> 00:22:26,900
So I asked some old maid to look
for it immediately,

438
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:30,100
and found Madam Li

439
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:32,100
learned this

440
00:22:32,140 --> 00:22:32,900
from a shop outside of the palace.

441
00:22:33,580 --> 00:22:35,060
So I asked them

442
00:22:35,060 --> 00:22:36,540
to get me the receipt

443
00:22:37,020 --> 00:22:40,500
and made some myself.

444
00:22:40,980 --> 00:22:43,580
His Majesty said the familiar taste

445
00:22:43,660 --> 00:22:45,620
is back in the palace again.

446
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:48,500
The taste is back in the palace again.

447
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:50,820
What taste?

448
00:22:51,820 --> 00:22:53,460
The taste of candied plum

449
00:22:53,460 --> 00:22:54,740
Madam Li made!

450
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:57,420
Have some, Your Majesty!

451
00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:07,460
Kindness of warm sun.

452
00:23:08,180 --> 00:23:11,100
Such kindness of warm sun, can’t be repaid by grass

453
00:23:12,380 --> 00:23:14,740
I asked someone to

454
00:23:14,740 --> 00:23:16,220
carve it onto the dish.

455
00:23:16,700 --> 00:23:18,540
Because when His Majesty tasted

456
00:23:18,580 --> 00:23:20,260
the candied plums,

457
00:23:20,460 --> 00:23:22,380
he said those two lines.

458
00:23:23,100 --> 00:23:23,980
I thought His Majesty must’ve

459
00:23:24,260 --> 00:23:26,340
been reminded of the love you gave him

460
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:29,020
when he was young

461
00:23:29,020 --> 00:23:30,900
by the plums.

462
00:23:31,580 --> 00:23:32,380
Idiot!

463
00:23:33,060 --> 00:23:35,140
If you are not smart enough to earn credits,

464
00:23:35,460 --> 00:23:36,220
and want to live,

465
00:23:36,780 --> 00:23:38,660
then keep your damn mouth shut!

466
00:23:52,380 --> 00:23:54,220
I lost my temper

467
00:23:55,140 --> 00:23:57,500
and shouted at a eunuch

468
00:23:58,300 --> 00:24:00,580
in front of Your Majesty and the Her Majesty.

469
00:24:01,780 --> 00:24:02,820
I disturbed your meeting

470
00:24:03,180 --> 00:24:04,980
with the Eempress.

471
00:24:06,580 --> 00:24:08,180
I’ve been in the palace for 20 years,

472
00:24:08,180 --> 00:24:09,580
yet I did such a disgraceful thing.

473
00:24:11,900 --> 00:24:13,700
I lost my mind.

474
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:15,340
I am guilty.

475
00:24:15,860 --> 00:24:18,180
Please punish me harshly

476
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:20,620
to warn others.

477
00:24:25,660 --> 00:24:26,540
Jichen,

478
00:24:27,660 --> 00:24:29,260
you’ve been with me for more than ten years.

479
00:24:30,700 --> 00:24:32,180
I know you.

480
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:35,140
You sacrificed your dignity

481
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:38,060
to protect me from losing my dignity

482
00:24:38,060 --> 00:24:39,340
in front of all the juniors.

483
00:24:41,700 --> 00:24:42,740
Get up, get up.

484
00:24:46,300 --> 00:24:47,540
I have fewer and fewer people around me

485
00:24:48,500 --> 00:24:51,020
who really understand me.

486
00:24:53,260 --> 00:24:56,260
Come on, talk with me.

487
00:25:02,060 --> 00:25:03,020
That day at the court,

488
00:25:03,500 --> 00:25:04,300
I acted on impulse

489
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:06,820
without thorough consideration.

490
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:09,620
Empress Dowager handled it easily.

491
00:25:11,540 --> 00:25:12,820
I planned for days

492
00:25:12,980 --> 00:25:14,540
to let the Empress to try it.

493
00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:17,380
As what Jinrui said,

494
00:25:17,860 --> 00:25:19,500
Ren Shouzhong behaved abnormally.

495
00:25:19,660 --> 00:25:20,940
I’m further confirmed that

496
00:25:21,860 --> 00:25:23,780
what my uncle said about my history

497
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:25,100
is true.

498
00:25:26,380 --> 00:25:29,420
And all the previous major officials

499
00:25:29,580 --> 00:25:30,620
know it.

500
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:36,900
Maoze,

501
00:25:37,540 --> 00:25:39,500
what do you think about it?

502
00:25:41,340 --> 00:25:42,580
I’m just an inferior servant

503
00:25:43,060 --> 00:25:44,940
who’s not qualified to comment on such a big issue.

504
00:25:46,740 --> 00:25:48,660
Even you can’t tell me the truth anymore.

505
00:25:50,460 --> 00:25:52,820
I just thought the Empress is honest
and straightforward,

506
00:25:53,220 --> 00:25:54,820
and she knows nothing about it.

507
00:25:55,420 --> 00:25:56,860
By doing that,

508
00:25:57,100 --> 00:25:58,060
she might

509
00:25:59,100 --> 00:26:00,500
have irritated Empress Dowager.

510
00:26:00,660 --> 00:26:01,540
Honest and straightforward?

511
00:26:01,980 --> 00:26:03,700
Why don’t you just call her stupid and reckless?

512
00:26:05,300 --> 00:26:06,580
Irritate her?

513
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:08,580
I want to show her

514
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:09,980
she found such a reckless woman

515
00:26:10,180 --> 00:26:11,500
for me

516
00:26:11,900 --> 00:26:12,860
as my legal wife!

517
00:26:14,900 --> 00:26:15,820
Maoze, tell me,

518
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:17,580
will my birth mother

519
00:26:18,060 --> 00:26:19,020
force me to marry

520
00:26:19,020 --> 00:26:20,100
a rude woman like her?

521
00:26:23,220 --> 00:26:25,700
I lost my parents when I was young,

522
00:26:26,380 --> 00:26:27,780
and raised by servants in the palace.

523
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:32,260
I don’t know how

524
00:26:32,540 --> 00:26:33,940
normal people choose wife and husband

525
00:26:34,100 --> 00:26:35,100
for their son and daughter.

526
00:26:36,660 --> 00:26:38,300
I was always scared of Empress Dowager
most since I was a kid.

527
00:26:39,180 --> 00:26:40,420
But I always thought

528
00:26:40,740 --> 00:26:42,380
she’s just being strict to me.

529
00:26:43,860 --> 00:26:45,540
We are all born in the royal family

530
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:47,260
who’s responsible for the whole state.

531
00:26:48,260 --> 00:26:50,180
So we can’t be intimate

532
00:26:50,660 --> 00:26:52,500
like normal mother and son.

533
00:26:54,140 --> 00:26:57,060
But who knows that’s why.

534
00:26:58,980 --> 00:26:59,980
When I was four,

535
00:27:00,740 --> 00:27:02,180
Granny Xu who cared for me most

536
00:27:02,420 --> 00:27:03,700
was evicted from the Palace

537
00:27:03,700 --> 00:27:04,580
because of some accusation.

538
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:06,660
Now thinking about it,

539
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:08,180
they must've been afraid

540
00:27:08,180 --> 00:27:09,180
that she'd tell me the truth.

541
00:27:09,300 --> 00:27:10,220
Your Majesty,

542
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:22,820
I have only you around me

543
00:27:23,460 --> 00:27:24,420
whom I can trust with all my heart.

544
00:27:25,860 --> 00:27:26,940
But these days

545
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:29,420
I was really scared and worried

546
00:27:29,580 --> 00:27:30,380
about you...

547
00:27:30,580 --> 00:27:31,300
For what?

548
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:33,580
Empress Dowager is annoyed

549
00:27:34,020 --> 00:27:36,460
and becomes suspicious of you.

550
00:27:36,660 --> 00:27:38,180
When I was young, my birth mother
was just around me,

551
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:39,860
yet I had no idea,

552
00:27:39,940 --> 00:27:41,060
seeing her as an inferior concubine.

553
00:27:42,180 --> 00:27:43,460
Now I know who she is,

554
00:27:43,780 --> 00:27:45,100
but I can’t take her back

555
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,380
and fulfill my filial piety.

556
00:27:47,180 --> 00:27:48,380
Now I just

557
00:27:48,460 --> 00:27:49,860
asked all the ladies in the Palace

558
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:52,260
to learn to make the dessert
and candied fruits she made,

559
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:54,380
trying to fool myself that

560
00:27:54,980 --> 00:27:56,580
taste is back to the Palace.

561
00:27:57,820 --> 00:28:00,140
And she will be annoyed just by that?

562
00:28:01,260 --> 00:28:03,620
Who should feel angry,

563
00:28:03,660 --> 00:28:04,620
me or her?

564
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:13,380
Back then, the late Emperor decided
to make me the Empress,

565
00:28:14,900 --> 00:28:16,300
then he needs a reason to

566
00:28:17,180 --> 00:28:18,860
have sons.

567
00:28:20,060 --> 00:28:21,580
He’d been sick for years,

568
00:28:23,420 --> 00:28:26,420
the court was filled with unclear
dangers and conflicts,

569
00:28:28,580 --> 00:28:29,900
if it wasn’t me,

570
00:28:31,220 --> 00:28:33,020
who can handle it?

571
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:39,300
If there’s a birth mother of the prince,

572
00:28:40,700 --> 00:28:42,140
how many people

573
00:28:42,260 --> 00:28:45,020
will form a power and bring chaos to the court?

574
00:28:46,460 --> 00:28:48,140
The decision he made

575
00:28:48,420 --> 00:28:50,140
is indeed a wise one.

576
00:28:54,180 --> 00:28:55,460
Before he died,

577
00:28:57,980 --> 00:29:01,580
he told me to guard the state for the Zhaos,

578
00:29:05,060 --> 00:29:07,900
to prepare it for his son,

579
00:29:10,300 --> 00:29:12,780
and to treat Lanhui nicely.

580
00:29:14,980 --> 00:29:17,380
I never failed to do so

581
00:29:22,100 --> 00:29:23,700
to thank his love to me for years.

582
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:28,180
But at that time,

583
00:29:28,660 --> 00:29:30,780
I asked him one question.

584
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,220
I asked,

585
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:40,540
many people know the truth.

586
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:43,900
If His Majesty found out

587
00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:46,620
and insisted on taking his birth mother back

588
00:29:48,580 --> 00:29:50,300
to the court,

589
00:29:51,020 --> 00:29:52,780
what should I do?

590
00:30:14,660 --> 00:30:15,620
Is the breakfast ready?

591
00:30:18,980 --> 00:30:20,260
I’ve been writing letters for quite some time.

592
00:30:20,460 --> 00:30:21,300
I feel really hungry.

593
00:30:23,380 --> 00:30:24,540
The breakfast is ready.

594
00:30:25,060 --> 00:30:27,180
Your Majesty, Ren Shouzhong is waiting outside.

595
00:30:28,060 --> 00:30:28,900
Why is he here?

596
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:30,380
The banquets

597
00:30:30,380 --> 00:30:31,340
will be held in the Court of Rarity today.

598
00:30:31,340 --> 00:30:33,260
Empress Dowager sends him to watch over.

599
00:30:33,660 --> 00:30:34,940
In case we will make some mistakes

600
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:35,900
since it’s our first time.

601
00:30:35,900 --> 00:30:37,100
It is the first time of yours,

602
00:30:37,260 --> 00:30:38,340
but not mine!

603
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:39,540
She thinks…

604
00:30:50,100 --> 00:30:51,580
Go, tell him

605
00:30:51,700 --> 00:30:53,660
I had headache last night, fell asleep late,

606
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:54,820
and will wake up later.

607
00:30:55,180 --> 00:30:56,620
Let them wait outside.

608
00:30:56,780 --> 00:30:57,580
Don’t let him in.

609
00:30:58,260 --> 00:30:58,980
Yes, Your Majesty.

610
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:11,620
= Jiang Deming =
Officer Jiang.

611
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:13,540
Come with me.

612
00:31:14,420 --> 00:31:16,060
I have some gifts for you.

613
00:31:16,180 --> 00:31:17,140
Maoze didn’t do anything

614
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:18,940
to deserve the gifts.

615
00:31:26,860 --> 00:31:30,180
You grow up in the Palace,

616
00:31:30,900 --> 00:31:32,540
and you’ve been serving His Majesty since seven.

617
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:35,420
You are loyal and smart,

618
00:31:36,060 --> 00:31:37,620
and His Majesty loves you

619
00:31:38,220 --> 00:31:41,180
and trusts you most.

620
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:43,660
Come with me.

621
00:31:45,020 --> 00:31:46,420
When the storm comes,

622
00:31:47,300 --> 00:31:48,780
there’s nowhere to hide.

623
00:31:50,500 --> 00:31:52,700
If you have help to resolve it,

624
00:31:53,700 --> 00:31:55,260
it will be your credit.

625
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:59,620
The thing I’m going to give you

626
00:32:00,820 --> 00:32:02,060
is an old item,

627
00:32:03,060 --> 00:32:04,540
which is connected to you.

628
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:08,020
Empress Dowager asked me to give it back.

629
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:30,340
What a good rebut!

630
00:32:30,580 --> 00:32:31,700
What a Scholar Yan!

631
00:32:32,220 --> 00:32:34,180
Because of the lack of talents,

632
00:32:34,300 --> 00:32:35,860
we can also have people with medium talents.

633
00:32:36,580 --> 00:32:38,500
What she did is insane!

634
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:40,260
She has already let

635
00:32:40,260 --> 00:32:41,540
Zhang Qi who helped her

636
00:32:41,540 --> 00:32:42,620
to take a position.

637
00:32:43,180 --> 00:32:45,300
Now she’s giving him a more important position?

638
00:32:45,820 --> 00:32:47,020
Is she going to make the court of the Zhaos

639
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:48,540
her family business?

640
00:32:52,180 --> 00:32:52,900
Go, leave.

641
00:32:53,460 --> 00:32:54,500
Don’t come tonight.

642
00:32:55,100 --> 00:32:57,900
Empress said she has something emergency to report.

643
00:32:58,580 --> 00:32:59,620
And Lady Shang

644
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:02,300
said she tried some new fruits,

645
00:33:02,500 --> 00:33:03,660
dried some pork

646
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:05,340
and warmed some wine,

647
00:33:05,580 --> 00:33:07,940
waiting for you to enjoy it.

648
00:33:08,060 --> 00:33:09,300
I don’t think I can sleep tonight

649
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:11,900
with so many reports to read.

650
00:33:12,580 --> 00:33:13,460
No matter what things they have

651
00:33:13,580 --> 00:33:15,300
can’t be more urgent than the state affairs.

652
00:33:34,660 --> 00:33:36,500
Maoze, the awards to my birth mother,

653
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:37,820
to Concubine Li,

654
00:33:38,220 --> 00:33:39,940
should’ve arrived by now.

655
00:33:40,220 --> 00:33:41,220
Did she see

656
00:33:41,380 --> 00:33:43,140
the hairpin, the ring and the silk flower?

657
00:33:44,060 --> 00:33:45,740
I asked someone to tint it with green feathers

658
00:33:46,020 --> 00:33:47,500
to embody the gratitude of grass.

659
00:33:48,020 --> 00:33:49,660
Did she say anything?

660
00:33:50,740 --> 00:33:53,260
I didn’t hear anything yet.

661
00:33:54,540 --> 00:33:55,940
Maybe it took longer than I expected.

662
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:58,740
Maybe it got delayed,

663
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:02,020
or maybe she’s thinking about what to reply,

664
00:34:02,340 --> 00:34:03,340
and still considering about it.

665
00:34:04,700 --> 00:34:06,220
I told you to buy more plums and biscuits

666
00:34:06,380 --> 00:34:07,660
from the store of Liang,

667
00:34:07,740 --> 00:34:08,420
did you get them?

668
00:34:16,100 --> 00:34:18,300
I didn’t go out of the Palace.

669
00:34:20,820 --> 00:34:21,940
You are always conscientious,

670
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:24,700
there must be a reason for you.

671
00:34:24,860 --> 00:34:25,860
Just tell me,

672
00:34:25,980 --> 00:34:27,060
why bother to kowtow.

673
00:34:30,820 --> 00:34:32,180
Forgive me, Your Majesty,

674
00:34:33,580 --> 00:34:35,420
but please bury your love to Madam Li

675
00:34:36,060 --> 00:34:37,100
deep down in your heart,

676
00:34:38,140 --> 00:34:39,020
and never do anything

677
00:34:39,500 --> 00:34:41,180
that annoys Empress Dowager again.

678
00:34:49,300 --> 00:34:50,460
Why even you are forcing me now?

679
00:34:52,980 --> 00:34:54,620
I made her angry

680
00:34:57,380 --> 00:34:58,780
because I knew the truth

681
00:34:59,460 --> 00:35:01,540
or because I talked about filial piety at court?

682
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:03,340
Why is she so angry

683
00:35:03,500 --> 00:35:05,020
at me?

684
00:35:07,940 --> 00:35:09,660
Because I missed

685
00:35:09,660 --> 00:35:10,900
some snack

686
00:35:11,180 --> 00:35:12,540
made by a concubine

687
00:35:13,300 --> 00:35:15,500
of the late Emperor?

688
00:35:17,860 --> 00:35:19,860
Well then, so what?

689
00:35:20,220 --> 00:35:21,740
Will she kill me or abolish me?

690
00:35:23,140 --> 00:35:24,460
She can’t leave you,

691
00:35:25,340 --> 00:35:27,100
nor can you.

692
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:29,100
Song can’t survive without

693
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:30,140
Your Majesty and Empress Dowager.

694
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:34,060
But it won’t change anything

695
00:35:35,500 --> 00:35:37,060
if Your Majesty have Concubine Li or not,

696
00:35:37,700 --> 00:35:40,620
or if Empress Dowager has Concubine Li

697
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:45,260
or if the country has Concubine Li or not.

698
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:48,060
What?

699
00:35:48,820 --> 00:35:50,220
His Majesty has refused to see me

700
00:35:50,860 --> 00:35:52,740
for more than half a month.

701
00:35:54,500 --> 00:35:55,940
I, as his legal wife,

702
00:35:56,740 --> 00:35:58,620
can’t even see him.

703
00:36:00,300 --> 00:36:01,740
He wasn’t intimate with me before,

704
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:04,580
but at least he treated me with due respect.

705
00:36:05,900 --> 00:36:09,500
But now Shang, Yang

706
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:11,220
and Sun,

707
00:36:11,900 --> 00:36:13,140
those bitches

708
00:36:14,700 --> 00:36:17,220
bewitch His Majesty

709
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,380
with all the tricks every day.

710
00:36:20,180 --> 00:36:21,580
The way they look at him

711
00:36:22,260 --> 00:36:23,900
is showing disrespect to me.

712
00:36:25,180 --> 00:36:26,780
Today, in the Imperial Garden,

713
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:31,500
Sun is only a few steps away,

714
00:36:32,060 --> 00:36:33,540
but she didn’t come to greet me.

715
00:36:35,580 --> 00:36:36,820
Instead, she pretended not to see me

716
00:36:36,820 --> 00:36:38,020
and just walked away.

717
00:36:39,420 --> 00:36:40,260
Your Majesty，

718
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:43,340
they are saying that

719
00:36:43,820 --> 00:36:48,340
His Majesty desolated me

720
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:52,740
because you forced him to marry me.

721
00:36:54,260 --> 00:36:57,220
Later, he hates me more

722
00:36:58,740 --> 00:37:00,700
because he knew you…

723
00:37:00,700 --> 00:37:01,540
Knew what?

724
00:37:03,100 --> 00:37:04,100
Hates me?

725
00:37:05,420 --> 00:37:06,660
I, I’m not...

726
00:37:06,660 --> 00:37:07,110
I...

727
00:37:07,180 --> 00:37:08,300
I’m...

728
00:37:09,460 --> 00:37:10,260
I...

729
00:37:11,100 --> 00:37:11,900
Yes,

730
00:37:13,620 --> 00:37:15,940
I forced him to marry you two years ago.

731
00:37:16,900 --> 00:37:18,540
Now you come here

732
00:37:19,100 --> 00:37:21,180
complaining that your husband does not love you

733
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,020
or respect you.

734
00:37:23,220 --> 00:37:24,300
Are you complaining

735
00:37:24,460 --> 00:37:26,020
that I shouldn’t have forced him to marry you?

736
00:37:27,740 --> 00:37:29,180
Or you want to tell me

737
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:31,100
he’s not filial to me?

738
00:37:32,460 --> 00:37:36,580
You want me to abolish his wife

739
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:39,340
or you want to ruin our relationship

740
00:37:39,340 --> 00:37:40,300
and turn us against each other?

741
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:44,220
Your Majesty,

742
00:37:44,220 --> 00:37:44,900
I...

743
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:47,620
I dare not.

744
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:49,940
When the late Emperor deceased,

745
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:52,140
my father was connected with the prime minister.

746
00:37:52,380 --> 00:37:53,220
and they confiscated the property
and exterminate my family.

747
00:37:53,900 --> 00:37:54,700
This jade cup

748
00:37:54,700 --> 00:37:56,020
was given to Officer Jiang.

749
00:37:56,380 --> 00:37:57,260
But today,

750
00:37:57,900 --> 00:38:00,700
Jiang gave it back to me.

751
00:38:08,740 --> 00:38:09,540
I remember

752
00:38:10,220 --> 00:38:11,180
the late Emperor was always sick

753
00:38:11,660 --> 00:38:12,620
and unable to attend the state affairs.

754
00:38:13,420 --> 00:38:15,180
Many officials had all kinds of thoughts

755
00:38:15,180 --> 00:38:16,180
and even put them into action.

756
00:38:16,660 --> 00:38:18,220
But no one can step beyond Empress Dowager.

757
00:38:18,940 --> 00:38:19,540
Those plans

758
00:38:19,580 --> 00:38:20,700
were just

759
00:38:20,700 --> 00:38:22,620
cases of rebellion and usurping,

760
00:38:23,060 --> 00:38:24,220
which killed and executed

761
00:38:24,300 --> 00:38:25,940
many lives in the Palace.

762
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,380
People were so scared.

763
00:38:28,620 --> 00:38:29,740
But I believe one thing

764
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:31,460
Officer Jiang said today.

765
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:33,340
What?

766
00:38:34,100 --> 00:38:35,540
Before the late Emperor died,

767
00:38:36,500 --> 00:38:37,460
she asked

768
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:39,020
if Your Majesty found out the truth,

769
00:38:39,020 --> 00:38:39,940
what should she do?

770
00:38:41,020 --> 00:38:41,900
He said

771
00:38:42,940 --> 00:38:44,020
no matter what happened,

772
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:45,740
we can’t have two mothers of the Emperor
exist in the palace.

773
00:38:48,700 --> 00:38:50,420
I don’t believe she dares to do so!

774
00:38:51,940 --> 00:38:52,980
After so many years,

775
00:38:53,300 --> 00:38:54,580
Concubine Li lives just fine.

776
00:38:55,260 --> 00:38:57,060
She got higher rankings and more awards.

777
00:38:57,540 --> 00:38:59,460
Although she was sent to the Mausoleum,

778
00:38:59,500 --> 00:39:00,420
but I checked

779
00:39:00,980 --> 00:39:03,220
that what she receives is more than concubines

780
00:39:03,220 --> 00:39:04,180
of the same ranking in the palace.

781
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:06,020
She used to give her own son

782
00:39:06,020 --> 00:39:07,700
to Empress Dowager,

783
00:39:08,180 --> 00:39:10,020
and never had any greediness.

784
00:39:11,020 --> 00:39:11,700
But now,

785
00:39:11,700 --> 00:39:13,300
she might be the one who

786
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:14,740
would cause chaos to the court.

787
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,820
She never had any greediness...

788
00:39:17,100 --> 00:39:17,900
Before, Concubine Li

789
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:19,300
never had any greediness.

790
00:39:19,660 --> 00:39:20,460
But now

791
00:39:21,060 --> 00:39:22,220
you are the Emperor

792
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:22,980
of the state

793
00:39:24,020 --> 00:39:25,940
If Concubine Li figured out that

794
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:27,580
you found the truth

795
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:30,140
and wanted something

796
00:39:30,180 --> 00:39:31,380
she deserves as a mother?

797
00:39:33,100 --> 00:39:34,700
Eighth Prince can’t get along with Empress Dowager,

798
00:39:35,220 --> 00:39:36,700
and now he told you this at this point,

799
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:37,820
what is he up to?

800
00:39:46,100 --> 00:39:47,700
I can force him to marry you,

801
00:39:48,100 --> 00:39:49,780
but not to love you.

802
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:52,500
I can give you the position,

803
00:39:53,100 --> 00:39:54,980
but not the respect.

804
00:39:56,020 --> 00:39:57,540
You want to get close to His Majesty,

805
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:58,900
but you are not smart,

806
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:00,340
obedient and virtuous,

807
00:40:00,940 --> 00:40:02,260
then what can I do?

808
00:40:19,620 --> 00:40:20,860
Your Majesty.

809
00:40:24,740 --> 00:40:25,500
I...

810
00:40:26,780 --> 00:40:28,300
I really don’t...

811
00:40:29,100 --> 00:40:30,780
don’t know what I should do.

812
00:40:31,220 --> 00:40:32,220
Your Majesty,

813
00:40:32,740 --> 00:40:34,700
I feel sad

814
00:40:34,940 --> 00:40:37,140
and depressed.

815
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:38,860
In this world,

816
00:40:39,900 --> 00:40:41,660
no one can stay happy every day.

817
00:40:43,740 --> 00:40:46,020
Everyone has depressing moments.

818
00:40:47,340 --> 00:40:48,780
If you want to earn what people are afraid of,

819
00:40:49,700 --> 00:40:51,340
you must be able to frighten them;

820
00:40:52,500 --> 00:40:53,820
if you want to earn others respect,

821
00:40:54,740 --> 00:40:56,460
you must have the virtue to earn them

822
00:41:02,780 --> 00:41:04,700
= The Analects of Confucius =

823
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:06,420
Reading might not help to manage the country,

824
00:41:07,940 --> 00:41:11,300
but can polish your character and calm you down.

825
00:41:31,460 --> 00:41:32,660
The hairpins and flowers Your Majesty bestowed

826
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:33,820
to Concubine Li

827
00:41:34,460 --> 00:41:36,100
was held up by Officer Jiang.

828
00:41:36,980 --> 00:41:38,620
He replaced them with the same thing

829
00:41:38,620 --> 00:41:40,460
other concubines received.

830
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:42,580
But,

831
00:41:45,140 --> 00:41:46,340
but he added a

832
00:41:46,460 --> 00:41:47,940
long hairpin bestowed by Empress Dowager.

833
00:41:49,780 --> 00:41:50,700
Officer Jiang said

834
00:41:50,820 --> 00:41:52,380
he knows he can be sentenced to death,

835
00:41:53,020 --> 00:41:54,020
and he’s waiting for your order.

836
00:41:54,540 --> 00:41:55,500
But Madam Li

837
00:41:55,700 --> 00:41:57,220
doesn’t know what happened in the Palace.

838
00:41:58,220 --> 00:42:00,380
She’s fully recovered

839
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:03,460
and calm as before.

840
00:42:06,340 --> 00:42:08,940
Great.

841
00:42:16,620 --> 00:42:17,340
I understand.

842
00:42:18,740 --> 00:42:21,060
I can’t do anything to Empress Dowager,

843
00:42:21,860 --> 00:42:24,140
nor can her.

844
00:42:25,140 --> 00:42:27,180
But the anger we have

845
00:42:27,580 --> 00:42:29,620
can be revealed to the whole court

846
00:42:31,660 --> 00:42:32,700
through other things and other people.

847
00:42:32,940 --> 00:42:34,180
Zhang Qi has no talent nor virtue.

848
00:42:34,860 --> 00:42:35,900
His only credit

849
00:42:36,100 --> 00:42:38,020
is to have kept Empress Dowager

850
00:42:38,020 --> 00:42:39,020
when she was in trouble.

851
00:42:39,940 --> 00:42:40,900
That credit

852
00:42:41,260 --> 00:42:42,620
has been rewarded by Empress Dowager many times

853
00:42:43,260 --> 00:42:44,740
with titles, houses, and treasure.

854
00:42:45,060 --> 00:42:46,900
But she never put him at an important position.

855
00:42:48,060 --> 00:42:49,020
But now she’s promoting Zhang Qi

856
00:42:49,140 --> 00:42:50,540
to the Privy Council Chief Executive.

857
00:42:51,620 --> 00:42:52,740
She did this to show me,

858
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:54,900
